{"tid":593453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"野豬渡維港 水陸兩路無敵手","createTime":"2018-03-15T04:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T06:44:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"769eb8da30aed6ab63eff548beebbb1ff9058dfb","tid":593453,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:06:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180315/20332466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180315%2F20332466&d=XioFzSu4gs%2FGinipWUyl0SwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=cd14cd1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180315%2F20332466&h=d2621401\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180315/20332466</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：野豬渡維港<br />\n水陸兩路無敵手 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n自從2011年維港渡海泳復辦，每年10月都有幾千人游水過海，何其壯觀。噚日就有泳手疑似提早足足半年試水&hellip;&hellip;咪住先，咁多毛嘅？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180315/large/a1404a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180315%2Flarge%2Fa1404a.gif&h=836bb12e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n野豬過海，唔使搭船，方便又快捷。<br />\n互聯網<br />\n<br />\n有網民前日喺西環碼頭吹風影相之際，發現呢位「野豬界歐鎧淳」悠然游向岸邊，睇嚟好有經驗，完全無視碼頭嘩嘩聲舉機影相拍片嘅遊人。野豬喺堅尼地城海旁搵到個位登陸，一上岸就走嚟走去搵嘢食。警察接報到場攞盾牌包圍，野豬嚇親之下急急腳橫過城西道，去卑路乍灣公園散步，途經車輛都要收慢避開，可憐阿Sir索晒氣，直到夜晚9點野豬先至落網，由漁護署人員運走。<br />\n<br />\n呢隻冇獠牙嘅野豬冇搶嘢食，又冇狂奔撞人，街坊都讚佢乖，不過亦有女士獨具慧眼，大嗌「呢隻黑毛豬嚟㗎」！"},{"pid":"52e9ef2693061cda46beb963860ec806aafd0adf","tid":593453,"uid":102096,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:07:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81bc39bc30b3b2b20cc5355b1b2d9372af9af55c","tid":593453,"uid":98232,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"769eb8da30aed6ab63eff548beebbb1ff9058dfb","tid":593453,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislik